                            <li class="mt-3">
                                <span class="text-success fw-bold">Ask the right questions:</span> Assess sellers by looking at the information in their profiles. Dig deeper by sending a message.
                            </li>
                            <li class="mt-3">
                                <span class="text-success fw-bold">Look at their badges:</span> Badges on a seller’s profile help you know what steps they took to prove they are a trusted partner.
                            </li>
