                                <span class="text-success fw-bold">Trade Assurance Supplier:</span> Gold suppliers who accept payment through Pakmart.com, enabling Pakmart.com payment and order protection.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                        <img src="~/images/vendr_selctn_prcss.jpg" class="img-fluid" alt="Vendor Selection Process" />
